Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是厚颜无耻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说得很嚣张吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.97,0:23:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和职业棋手对局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦处于劣势
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很难扳回的
